		<title>18 Great Positioning Statement Examples + How to Write One (with Templates)</title>
		<link>https://www.wordstream.com/blog/positioning-statement</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Kristen McCormick]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Mon, 21 Oct 2024 15:16:59 +0000</pubDate>
				<category><![CDATA[Copywriting]]></category>
