										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Artificial intelligence helps you create better marketing copy faster. That is, if you know how to use it and which AI copywriting tools to use.</p>
<p>We did the legwork, reviewing and trialing dozens of platforms to create a list of the best AI copywriting tools available. In our search, we also found several interesting free tools that‚Äôll help you tackle specific copywriting jobs. Read on to see what we found.</p>
<h3>Contents</h3>
<ul>
<li><a href="#How-do-AI-copywriting-tools-work">How do AI copywriting tools work?</a></li>
<li><a href="#Great-uses-for-AI-copywriting-tools">Great uses for AI copywriting tools</a></li>
<li><a href="#Best-AI-copywriting-tools">Best AI copywriting tools (that aren‚Äôt ChatGPT)</a></li>
<li><a href="#Best-free-AI-copywriting-tools">Best free AI copywriting tools</a></li>
<li><a href="#Tips-to-get-high-quality-copy-from-AI-copywriting-tools">Tips to get high-quality copy from AI copywriting tools</a></li>
<li><a href="#AI-copywriting-tools-FAQs">AI copywriting tools FAQs</a></li>
</ul>
<div id="How-do-AI-copywriting-tools-work"></div>
<h2>How do AI copywriting tools work?</h2>
<p>AI copywriting tools are software that combines machine learning algorithms with huge collections of existing content to produce human-sounding marketing copy. You can then use that copy to inspire your own <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2015/02/09/how-to-write-a-blog-post">blog posts</a>, landing page content, <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2021/07/01/email-marketing-tips">marketing emails</a>, and even entire <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/how-to-write-an-ebook">ebooks</a>.</p>
<p>The big difference between AI and other software is that AI has a sort of algorithmic intuition. It can comprehend and respond in a more human-like way and learn from each interaction.</p>
<p>Here‚Äôs an example. Let‚Äôs say you‚Äôre stuck on writing a blog post headline about the best <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/seo-copywriting">SEO copywriting</a> tools (relatable) so you write a <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2023/05/08/chatgpt-prompts">prompt</a> in casual language asking for help.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/best-ai-copywriting-tools-chatgpt3.webp" alt="AI copywriting tools - ChatGPT screeshot" width="936" height="485" class="aligncenter wp-image-79969 size-full" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/best-ai-copywriting-tools-chatgpt3.webp 936w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/best-ai-copywriting-tools-chatgpt3-480x249.webp 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 936px, 100vw" /></p>
<p>Interesting, but I want a little more humor.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/best-ai-copywriting-tools-google-chatgpt2.webp" alt="AI copywriting tools - Second chatgpt screenshot" width="936" height="600" class="aligncenter wp-image-79970 size-full" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/best-ai-copywriting-tools-google-chatgpt2.webp 936w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/best-ai-copywriting-tools-google-chatgpt2-480x308.webp 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 936px, 100vw" /></p>
<p>Not ready for publication yet. And it ignored my request to remove the colons. But the point is, we didn‚Äôt have to start over. The AI can take context from our first interaction and continue from there.</p>
<p>There are dozens of AI copywriting tools designed to solve a variety of challenges. But for the most part, they all take a <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ai-prompts-for-social-media">prompt</a>, review large libraries of content, and iterate on a response that‚Äôs more human-like than robot.</p>
<p><img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/16.0.1/72x72/1f6d1.png" alt="üõë" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /> Writing ads is tough. Use this free <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/google-adwords?cid=Web_Any_InContentTextLink_PPC_AWGrader_AWGrader">Google Ads Grader</a> and get an instant audit of your account to make sure all that work isn‚Äôt going to waste.</p>
<div id="Great-uses-for-AI-copywriting-tools"></div>
<h2>Great uses for AI copywriting tools</h2>
<p>It‚Äôs best <em>not</em> to think of AI as a <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2023/07/19/copywriting-skills">copywriter</a>, but as a partner that helps you write better copy more efficiently. Sure, AI can blurt out a whole blog post from a single <a href="https://localiq.com/blog/ai-prompt-examples/">prompt</a>, but it probably won‚Äôt be very good. And it may even be <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2023/06/28/ai-for-marketing">flat out false</a>.</p>
<p>Here are a handful of ways <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2023/06/05/generative-ai-in-digital-marketing">AI can help</a> you create better copy faster:</p>
<ul>
<li><strong>Ideation:</strong> Ask your AI tool to suggest 10 blog ideas around a particular topic.</li>
<li><strong>A/B testing:</strong> Use AI to create a few variants of <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/how-to-write-great-advertising-copy">ad copy</a> to test.</li>
<li><strong>SEO:</strong> AI tools can help you <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2023/09/05/chatgpt-seo">improve SEO</a> by suggesting how to incorporate keywords into a blog post.</li>
<li><strong>Meta descriptions:</strong> Some AI <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/website-copywriting">copywriting</a> tools can review an image and suggest <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/meta-description">meta descriptions</a> for it.</li>
<li><strong>Busting writer‚Äôs block:</strong> If you get stuck on how to phrase a description or write a header, prompt your AI tool to give you some alternatives.</li>
<li>Crafting competitive ad copy: Writing competitive Google Ads is tough, but <a href="https://localiq.com/blog/google-ads-ai-copy-tool/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">AI copy tools</a> can make it a breeze.</li>
<li><strong>Surfacing stats:</strong> Ask your AI tool to give you current statistics that support a claim (just make sure you verify them).</li>
<li><strong>Summarizing content:</strong> Many AI tools can pull a transcript from a video or voice recording and create a bullet-point summary.</li>
</ul>
<p>Not every AI copywriting tool is built for every job. Let‚Äôs look at some of the best tools available and where to <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ai-in-marketing">use AI</a>.</p>
<div id="Best-AI-copywriting-tools"></div>
<h2>Best AI copywriting tools (that aren‚Äôt ChatGPT)</h2>
<p>These are some of the best AI copywriting tools based on their popularity and from our own experience. We left ChatGPT off this list since it gets a lot of coverage. Plus, we‚Äôve already <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2023/03/06/how-to-use-chatgpt-for-small-business-marketing">written about it</a>.</p>
<h3>Copy.ai</h3>
<p><a href="http://copy.ai" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Copy.ai</a> is purpose-built to automate sales and marketing functions‚Äîand this includes a bucketload of tools for copywriters. You can use it to inspire outlines, briefs, <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2014/01/09/social-media-marketing-strategies">social media posts</a>, and even personalized marketing emails.</p>
<p>Workflows on Copy.ai make everything plug-and-play. Each workflow is made for a specific purpose, like ideating Facebook posts.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/best-ai-copywriting-tools-google-workflow.webp" alt="AI copywriting tools - screenshot of a Copy.ai workflow" width="936" height="485" class="aligncenter wp-image-79971 size-full" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/best-ai-copywriting-tools-google-workflow.webp 936w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/best-ai-copywriting-tools-google-workflow-480x249.webp 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 936px, 100vw" /></p>
<p>You just enter information about your keyword, target audience, and so on. In this case, Copy.AI gave us several ad options based on different <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2020/04/16/copywriting-formulas">copywriting frameworks</a>, like problem, agitate, solve (PAS).</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/best-ai-copywriting-tools-google-PAS.webp" alt="AI copywriting tools - Copy.ai output" width="936" height="510" class="aligncenter wp-image-79972 size-full" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/best-ai-copywriting-tools-google-PAS.webp 936w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/best-ai-copywriting-tools-google-PAS-480x262.webp 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 936px, 100vw" /></p>
<h4>Cool features</h4>
<ul>
<li>Large prompt library</li>
<li>Over 90 copywriting tools and workflows</li>
<li>Summarize-to-brief tool to turn transcripts into content briefs</li>
<li>Personalized email creator</li>
<li>Automated content refreshing</li>
</ul>
<h4>Pricing</h4>
<p>Copy.AI offers several pricing tiers that depend on the number of users and how much you‚Äôll use the tool.</p>
<p>The two least expensive are:</p>
<ul>
<li><strong>Free:</strong> one user, 2,000 words per month, 200 bonus credits to use on other activities</li>
<li><strong>Pro:</strong> $36 / month for five users, unlimited words, and 500 workflow credits</li>
</ul>
<h3>Jasper.ai</h3>
<p><a href="http://jasper.ai" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Jasper.AI</a> is another popular tool for copywriters that‚Äôs built on top of <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2023/03/06/how-to-use-chatgpt-for-small-business-marketing">ChatGPT3</a>. Jasper helps you create new content and upgrade things you‚Äôve already written. It‚Äôs designed for collaboration and integration so it‚Äôll fit fluidly into how you already work.</p>
<p>Jasper lets you create all the expected written content (blog posts, emails, etc.), and it also generates images to support your campaigns.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/best-ai-copywriting-tools-images.webp" alt="AI copywriting tools - four images created by jasper.ai" width="929" height="600" class="aligncenter wp-image-79973 size-full" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/best-ai-copywriting-tools-images.webp 929w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/best-ai-copywriting-tools-images-480x310.webp 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 929px, 100vw" /></p>
<p>There are several styles of content you can create like photography, acrylic paint, and ink. Just remember to closely review any image you plan to post. AI is notorious for making small mistakes like the conjoined hands in the top left image here. You want to speed up your work, not give your readers nightmares.</p>
<h4>Cool features</h4>
<ul>
<li>Plagiarism checker</li>
<li>Writing templates</li>
<li>Google Docs integration</li>
<li>Collaborative content calendar</li>
<li>Prompt enhancer</li>
</ul>
<h4>Pricing</h4>
<p>Jasper lets you kick the tool‚Äôs tires with a <a href="https://app.jasper.ai/?_gl=1*bwq1fn*_gcl_au*MTI3NTA4OTU5LjE3MDYwNTA4NTc.*_ga*Njc0MjE0Nzg4LjE3MDYwNTA4NTc.*_ga_D4P3CS8W5P*MTcwNjg5MzkzNy40LjEuMTcwNjg5NDUzMC43LjAuMA.." target="_blank" rel="noopener">free trial</a>. After that, <a href="https://www.jasper.ai/pricing" target="_blank" rel="noopener">pricing tiers</a> are built around the number of users and access to different features (e.g. art creation isn‚Äôt offered in the Creator plan).</p>
<ul>
<li><strong>Creator:</strong> $39 / month for one user and one brand voice</li>
<li><strong>Pro:</strong> $59 / month for five users, three brand voices, and more features (including art creation)</li>
</ul>
<h3>Breeze Content Agent</h3>
<p>All AI copywriting tools use training data to learn how to write. <a href="https://www.hubspot.com/products/content/content-ai-agent">Breeze Content Agent by HubSpot</a> stands out because it pulls data directly from your CRM. That means it‚Äôs trained to create hyper-relevant copy for your existing and potential customers.</p>
<p>When you fire up Breeze Content Agent to write a case study, blog post, or landing page, it‚Äôll know to include your target audience&#8217;s language and pain points. That‚Äôll make sure each asset you create with it has your brand voice, core values, and industry lingo baked in.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/ai-copywriting-tools-wordstream-breeze-1024x651.webp" alt="AI copywriting tools - screenshot of Breeze Content Agent." width="1024" height="651" class="aligncenter wp-image-90321 size-large" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/ai-copywriting-tools-wordstream-breeze-1024x651.webp 1024w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/ai-copywriting-tools-wordstream-breeze-300x191.webp 300w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/ai-copywriting-tools-wordstream-breeze-768x488.webp 768w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/ai-copywriting-tools-wordstream-breeze-1536x976.webp 1536w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/ai-copywriting-tools-wordstream-breeze-1080x686.webp 1080w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/ai-copywriting-tools-wordstream-breeze-1280x813.webp 1280w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/ai-copywriting-tools-wordstream-breeze-980x623.webp 980w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/ai-copywriting-tools-wordstream-breeze-480x305.webp 480w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/ai-copywriting-tools-wordstream-breeze-png.webp 1701w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></p>
<h4>Cool features</h4>
<ul>
<li>Brand voice editor</li>
<li>One-click SEO title and meta description generator</li>
<li>Personalized content created based on your CRM data</li>
<li>Landing page image creator (just enter relevant keywords)</li>
<li>Podcast show notes and blog outlines can be created based on keywords</li>
</ul>
<h4>Pricing</h4>
<p>Breeze Content Agent is included with the Content Hub Pro and Enterprise plans.</p>
<ul>
<li><strong>Pro plan:</strong> starts at $450 / month (includes three seats)</li>
<li><strong>Enterprise:</strong> starts at $1,500 / mo (includes five seats)</li>
</ul>
<h3>Describly</h3>
<p><a href="https://describely.ai/?__hstc=240231260.8c6b922a31f89c9124f307179ce21302.1706806585518.1706806585518.1706897507967.2&amp;__hssc=240231260.1.1706897507967&amp;__hsfp=272456965" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Describly</a> is part of the <a href="https://copysmith.ai/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Copysmith</a> bundle of AI copywriting tools that also include <a href="https://www.frase.io/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Frase</a> (SEO) and <a href="https://rytr.me/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Ryter</a> (writing assistant). Describly‚Äôs superpower is quickly creating or improving <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2019/06/26/product-descriptions">product descriptions</a>, titles, and tags for <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2021/02/18/ecommerce-tools-for-local-business">ecommerce</a> websites. The copy it creates is brand-aligned and designed for SEO.</p>
<p>The beauty of Describly is in its singular focus. You don‚Äôt have to wade through several menus or pick out the right features. You just connect a catalog and work right from the home screen.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/best-ai-copywriting-tools-describly2.webp" alt="AI copywriting tools - screenshot of describly's tool " width="936" height="317" class="aligncenter wp-image-79974 size-full" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/best-ai-copywriting-tools-describly2.webp 936w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/best-ai-copywriting-tools-describly2-480x163.webp 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 936px, 100vw" /></p>
<p>You can either start from scratch to have Describly write product descriptions for you. Or you can give it what you already have and ask it to tweak for a new tone. So when your CMO says to make all 8,000 product descriptions ‚Äúfunnier,‚Äù you‚Äôll have it done before lunch.</p>
<h4>Cool features</h4>
<ul>
<li>Integrates with WooCommerce, Google Ads, and other platforms</li>
<li>One-click online catalog updates</li>
<li>Approval workflow</li>
<li>Built-in review moderation</li>
<li>Premade templates</li>
</ul>
<h4>Pricing</h4>
<p>Describly offers one flat monthly price and ‚ÄúPower Ups‚Äù for additional usage.</p>
<ul>
<li><strong>Base:</strong> $28 / month for unlimited AI descriptions of up to 50 products plus unlimited store connectors and product uploads.</li>
<li><strong>Powerups:</strong> 55 cents per additional credit</li>
</ul>
<h3>QuillBot</h3>
<p>If you‚Äôre looking to zhuzh up content you‚Äôve already written, then <a href="https://quillbot.com/?utm_medium=cpc&amp;utm_source=bing&amp;utm_campaign=FA%20-%20HY%20%7C%20PERF%20-%20Search%20%7C%20General%20-%20Brand%20%7C%20PREM%20%7C%20CPA&amp;utm_term=quillbot&amp;utm_content=83150868354979&amp;campaign_type=search-428285966&amp;click_id=de4aefa4dc3218846c408a65e63b565c&amp;campaign_id=428285966&amp;adgroup_id=1330410514452880&amp;ad_id=83150868354979&amp;keyword=quillbot&amp;target=kwd-83151582213072:aud-808307753:loc-190&amp;network=o&amp;msclkid=de4aefa4dc3218846c408a65e63b565c" target="_blank" rel="noopener">QuillBot</a> is a great AI copywriting tool for you. Just give it a piece of copy and ask it to check for grammatical errors, shorten or expand it, or reword it with a different tone.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/best-ai-copywriting-tools-google-Quillbot.webp" alt="AI copywriting tools - QuillBot screenshot" width="936" height="508" class="aligncenter wp-image-79975 size-full" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/best-ai-copywriting-tools-google-Quillbot.webp 936w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/best-ai-copywriting-tools-google-Quillbot-480x261.webp 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 936px, 100vw" /></p>
<p>QuillBot is also useful for paraphrasing long, challenging content. Say you&#8217;ve been asked to write a post based on a lengthy research report. Paste the report into the QuillBot‚Äôs text box and it will produce a quick summary with bullet points.</p>
<h4>Cool features</h4>
<ul>
<li>Synonym finder</li>
<li>AI web research tool</li>
<li>Citation generator</li>
<li>Co-writing sentence completer</li>
<li>Chrome extension</li>
</ul>
<h4>Pricing</h4>
<p>Just like the tool itself, QuillBot‚Äôs pricing is simple and straightforward. There are just two pricing tiers differentiated by the number of words you can paraphrase and the features you have access to.</p>
<ul>
<li><strong>Free:</strong> 125 words in paraphrase, standard, and fluency modes</li>
<li><strong>Premium:</strong> $8.33 / month for unlimited words, eight modes (academic, formal, etc.), synonym slider</li>
</ul>
<h3>Writesonic</h3>
<p><a href="https://writesonic.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Writesonic</a> is a bit of a Swiss army knife of an AI copywriting tool. Use it to create content for blogs, chatbots, and ads as well as video, images, and even audio assets. It also has a paraphrasing tool, a text summarizer, and an <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2015/04/30/seo-basics">SEO</a> checker.</p>
<p>One of the most powerful features of Writesonic is its <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/great-landing-pages">landing page</a> creator. With a few descriptions and product features, you get a basic landing page that‚Äôs ready to be tweaked.</p>
<p>Writesonic will create full descriptions of each feature you enter and even add a surprisingly relevant call-to-action button.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/best-ai-copywriting-tools-google-landing-page.webp" alt="AI copywriting tools - landing page created by writesonic" width="936" height="462" class="aligncenter wp-image-79976 size-full" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/best-ai-copywriting-tools-google-landing-page.webp 936w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/best-ai-copywriting-tools-google-landing-page-480x237.webp 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 936px, 100vw" /></p>
<h4>Cool features</h4>
<ul>
<li>Voice commands or standard text inputs</li>
<li>25 languages available</li>
<li>Publish directly to Shopify, WordPress, or Wix</li>
<li>Built-in templates</li>
<li>Easy interface</li>
</ul>
<h4>Pricing</h4>
<p>Writesonic has a basic free version that‚Äôll let you test out the interface, but the paid plans give you a lot for the money.</p>
<ul>
<li><strong>Free:</strong> Content created by ChatGPT-3.5 (the free one), 10k words, and several integrations.</li>
<li><strong>Small Team:</strong> $13 / month for content from ChatGPT-4 (which costs to access directly), up to 20k words, and several additional features.</li>
</ul>
