<div id="Best-free-AI-copywriting-tools"></div>
<h2>Best free AI copywriting tools</h2>
<p>Many of the tools above have some type of free option, but they‚Äôre restricted by the features you get to use or the amount you can use them. The tools we‚Äôve listed here have robust free tiers (or are completely free, loke <a href="https://localiq.com/blog/how-to-use-google-bard/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Google Bard</a>) and are used for more specific use cases. You won‚Äôt burn through free credits quickly if you‚Äôre only using the tool to write press releases or an <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2016/05/27/guide-to-about-us-pages">About Us</a> page.</p>
<h3>HeroGuide</h3>
<p><a href="https://www.heroguide.ai/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">HeroGuide</a> is a cool little tool that writes up a brand story for your business. Just enter a description of what you do, the problems you solve, and who you solve them for. The AI then writes several versions of your brand story.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/best-ai-copywriting-tools-google-heroguide-2.webp" alt="AI copywriting tools - screenshot of HeroGuide output" width="765" height="600" class="aligncenter wp-image-79977 size-full" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/best-ai-copywriting-tools-google-heroguide-2.webp 765w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/best-ai-copywriting-tools-google-heroguide-2-480x376.webp 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 765px, 100vw" /></p>
<h4>What you get for free</h4>
<p>HeroGuide is a simple tool with zero bells and whistles, but you can use it an unlimited number of times completely for free.</p>
<h3>Great Headlines</h3>
<p><a href="https://greatheadlines.ai/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Great Headlines</a> is a free AI copywriting tool that promises to help you ‚ÄúWrite headlines like Don Draper in just a few seconds.‚Äù You‚Äôll feed the software your content, the target audience, and headline style. Then add some optional parameters like a call to action and brand voice.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/best-ai-copywriting-tools-google-headline.webp" alt="AI copywriting tools - headlines written by Great headlines" width="675" height="600" class="aligncenter wp-image-79978 size-full" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/best-ai-copywriting-tools-google-headline.webp 675w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/best-ai-copywriting-tools-google-headline-480x427.webp 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 675px, 100vw" /></p>
<h4>What you get for free</h4>
<p>You get the whole tool for free (there‚Äôs not even a request for an email address). You can also sign up for notifications about the upcoming premium version.</p>
<h3>LocaliQ&#8217;s Google Ads AI Copy Tool</h3>
<p>Google Ads delivers a great return for the money, but writing an endless stream of copy for them can be exhausting. Plus, search engine results pages are highly competitive, so you&#8217;ll need multiple variations of each ad to see which works best. That&#8217;s where the <a href="https://localiq.com/google-ads-ai-copy-tool/?cid=Web_LiQ_InContent_AICopyTool_AICT&amp;itm_source=localiq&amp;itm_medium=blog&amp;itm_campaign=incontent_links">Google Ads Copy Tool</a> comes in. Just enter a few details like your business name, target keywords, industry, etc., and the copy tool creates both Google Ads headlines and ad descriptions based on that information.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/google-ads-ai-copy-tool-wordstream-screenshot.webp" alt="AI tools - screenshot of the Google Ads AI Copy Tool." width="749" height="862" class="aligncenter wp-image-89926 size-full" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/google-ads-ai-copy-tool-wordstream-screenshot.webp 749w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/google-ads-ai-copy-tool-wordstream-screenshot-480x552.webp 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 749px, 100vw" /></p>
<p>You even get 10 variations of headlines and descriptions for each request, so there are plenty of options for testing.</p>
<h3>Newsletter.ai</h3>
<p><a href="https://newswriter.ai/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Newsletter.ai</a> writes first-draft press releases based on whatever event you‚Äôd like to promote. It‚Äôs a simple tool that can also improve a press release you‚Äôve already written. Once you give it the details, you‚Äôll get an email with a link and a code to access your press release draft. The tool‚Äôs creators recommend you edit the output (like you would with any AI writing).</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/best-ai-copywriting-tools-newswriter.webp" alt="AI copywriting tools - press release written by newsletter.ai" width="588" height="600" class="aligncenter wp-image-79979 size-full" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/best-ai-copywriting-tools-newswriter.webp 588w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/best-ai-copywriting-tools-newswriter-480x490.webp 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 588px, 100vw" /></p>
<h4>What you get for free</h4>
<p>There‚Äôs no noted limit on the number of press releases you can create for free using newswriter.ai. The tool is mostly a <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2021/06/15/lead-magnet-ideas">lead magnet</a> for the company‚Äôs press release <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/content-distribution">distribution</a> services.</p>
<h3>Writetone</h3>
<p><a href="https://writetone.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Writetone</a> paraphrases existing content or generates new copy for several marketing channels like social media, blogs, and email. In fact, the tool has dozens of use cases and industries to pick from depending on where you‚Äôre writing and for whom. So if you need a <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2018/12/03/cold-email">cold email</a> sequence written for mechanical engineers, Writetone has you covered.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/best-ai-copywriting-tools-google-writetone.webp" alt="AI copywriting tools - Screenshot of Writetone" width="936" height="484" class="aligncenter wp-image-79980 size-full" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/best-ai-copywriting-tools-google-writetone.webp 936w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/best-ai-copywriting-tools-google-writetone-480x248.webp 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 936px, 100vw" /></p>
<h4>What you get for free</h4>
<p>Writetone has paid tiers, but we added it here because of how robust the free option is. You have access to the full library of features, tones, and content types with no charge. And you can create or update 30,000 characters (around 12 pages) of copy every month.</p>
<div id="Tips-to-get-high-quality-copy-from-AI-copywriting-tools"></div>
<h2>How do you get high-quality copy from AI copywriting tools?</h2>
<p>Once you‚Äôve picked some AI copywriting tools to try out, it‚Äôll help to have a plan for how to use them.</p>
<h3>Use AI as a starting point</h3>
<p>There are marketers using AI tools to <a href="https://twitter.com/RossHudgens/status/1729889490947518868" target="_blank" rel="noopener">scrape blog topics</a> from existing websites and create hundreds of posts in a few days for quick traffic. But those gains are sometimes short-lived as Google can cut off the traffic to low-value content in an instant.</p>
<p>The better strategy is to use AI as a writing partner to bounce ideas off of. Ask it to rewrite something you‚Äôre struggling with. Or get a list of headlines that might offer a word or structure you hadn‚Äôt thought of.</p>
<h3>Factcheck and edit</h3>
<p>Not all AI tools have the latest content to learn from. Much of the verbiage they choose sounds bland. And sometimes they provide false information.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/best-ai-copywriting-tools-google-false.webp" alt="AI copywriting tools - Chatgpt response with incorrect data" width="613" height="600" class="aligncenter wp-image-79981 size-full" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/best-ai-copywriting-tools-google-false.webp 613w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/best-ai-copywriting-tools-google-false-480x470.webp 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 613px, 100vw" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://twitter.com/indranil_leo/status/1608548534386565120?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw%7Ctwcamp%5Etweetembed%7Ctwterm%5E1608548534386565120%7Ctwgr%5E40bef6128b6180cfabce993a97bfb7f8f1977adb%7Ctwcon%5Es1_&amp;ref_url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wordstream.com%2Fblog%2Fws%2F2023%2F06%2F28%2Fai-for-marketing" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Source</em></a></p>
<p>That‚Äôs why it‚Äôs critical that you closely review and edit any AI-generated content. And as we‚Äôve seen, that goes doubly true for images.</p>
<h3>Add personal experience and original data</h3>
<p>Your goal as a marketer is rarely to blend in. To stand out against a sea of AI sameness, you‚Äôll need to interject some original statistics, unique stories, and a voice that doesn‚Äôt sound like the exact tone everyone else will get from their AI tools.</p>
<p>In fact, the increased importance of original data and experiences was one of the top<a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/content-marketing-trends-2024"> content marketing trends</a> we noticed.</p>
<div id="AI-copywriting-tools-FAQs"></div>
<h2>FAQs about AI copywriting tools</h2>
<p>We covered a lot of ground. But there are a few questions we see a lot and are worth answering on their own.</p>
<h3>Which is the best tool for AI copywriting?</h3>
<p>This is a bit like asking which is the best hammer. Each tool has features and use cases that fit different needs and users. To find yours, start with the descriptions we gave above, and trial a few to see which suits your needs best.</p>
<h3>Is AI copywriting legal?</h3>
<p>It‚Äôs currently legal to use content created by AI as long as it doesn‚Äôt directly copy another copyrighted work verbatim. There are <a href="https://www.nytimes.com/2023/12/27/business/media/new-york-times-open-ai-microsoft-lawsuit.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">lawsuits</a> and <a href="https://www.axios.com/2024/01/02/copyright-law-violation-artificial-intelligence-courts" target="_blank" rel="noopener">legality discussions</a> in the works that could change how AI content is regulated, though. For now, it‚Äôs best to use a plagiarism checker to make sure your AI tool hasn‚Äôt drafted a nearly exact copy of something that already exists.</p>
<h3>Can Google detect AI copywriting?</h3>
<p><a href="https://developers.google.com/search/blog/2023/02/google-search-and-ai-content" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Google suggests</a> that its systems can identify AI content. However, as long as the search engine deems the copy to be high quality (and meeting its <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2023/07/14/google-e-e-a-t">E-E-A-T standards</a>), it‚Äôs allowed and will not be punished on search engine results pages.</p>
<h2>Find your ideal AI copywriting tool</h2>
<p>AI copywriting tools take on lots of forms for many different functions. The key to finding the right one to <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/copywriting-101">improve your copy</a> is structured experimentation.</p>
<p>Start by laying out the most challenging and friction-filled parts of your job. Look for <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/best-ai-tools">AI tools</a> with features to meet them. Then test each one for its output and user interface. This process will make sure you‚Äôre choosing software that solves your unique challenges.</p>
<p>Here are the best overall AI copywriting tools:</p>
<ul>
<li>Copy.ai</li>
<li>Jasper.ai</li>
<li>Breeze Content Agent</li>
<li>Describly</li>
<li>QuillBot</li>
<li>Writesonic</li>
</ul>
<p>Here are the best free AI copywriting tools:</p>
<ul>
<li>HeroGuide</li>
<li>Great Headlines</li>
<li>Newsletter.ai</li>
<li>LocaliQ&#8217;s Google Ads Copy Tool</li>
<li>Writetone</li>
</ul>
